[A range of pathogens, including fungi, bacteria, viruses and nematodes, have been reported previously to affect rice crops in the region. The symptoms described above are not sufficient for diagnosis, but reliable diagnosis of the cause and/or pathogen(s) associated with the problems is essential before any management strategies can be designed.

